# Corpus payloads / raw + extracted data — local-only per
# .squad/decisions.md "Raw archive storage = local disk only" ADR
# and docs/data-pipeline.md §80 ("Nothing in data/ is committed to git").
# Code, schemas, docs, configs, source inventories, manifests/templates,
# checksums, and tiny rights-cleared fixtures live in-repo; everything
# else under data/ stays local.
/data/
*.warc
*.warc.gz
